{"TopicId":207022,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"KSP 2: wish-lists compilation (I probably stole your idea!)","CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-02-22T19:42:19Z","PageNum":4,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Zozaf Kerman","CreatedById":219910,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-26T20:56:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpinlaunchers would be super cool. You\u2019ll probably be able to make these even if it\u2019s not a stock part though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-04-26T20:56:52Z\u0022 title=\u002204/26/2022 08:56  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EApril 26, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Zozaf Kerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EEgap wen kool yeh\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MARL_Mk1","CreatedById":192535,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-26T22:06:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFully working IVA. You should be able to do everything from inside your cockpit and control panels (maybe except mapview).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Barel","CreatedById":206148,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-26T22:20:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224123105\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221651010801\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192535\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lijazos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, Lijazos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFully working IVA. You should be able to do everything from inside your cockpit and control panels (maybe except mapview).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaving something like the ASET IVA replacements in stock would be awesome\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Laxez","CreatedById":216956,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-27T13:35:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224123070\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221651004960\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022137773\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Catto\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Catto said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about mass drivers? If that\u0027s too hightech, Spinlaunchers? We should have a way to not waste propellant and get stuff into space.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nor a SPACE ELEVATOR\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:heart_eyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/heart_eyes.png\u0022 title=\u0022:heart_eyes:\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003Enever gonna happen\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Catto","CreatedById":137773,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-27T13:59:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224123310\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221651066500\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Laxez\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, Laxez said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nor a SPACE ELEVATOR\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:heart_eyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/heart_eyes.png\u0022 title=\u0022:heart_eyes:\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003Enever gonna happen\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wish.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerb24","CreatedById":214340,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-27T19:00:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224123310\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221651066500\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Laxez\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Laxez said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nor a SPACE ELEVATOR\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:heart_eyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/heart_eyes.png\u0022 title=\u0022:heart_eyes:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean you can probably build one in KSP already. It just needs to be built on Gilly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-27T19:21:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224123425\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221651086047\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022214340\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerb24\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, Kerb24 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224123310\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221651066500\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Laxez\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Laxez said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nor a SPACE ELEVATOR\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:heart_eyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/heart_eyes.png\u0022 title=\u0022:heart_eyes:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean you can probably build one in KSP already. It just needs to be built on Gilly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPretty sure there are a few hills on Gilly that qualify as space elevators.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Laxez","CreatedById":216956,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-27T20:11:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224123425\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221651086047\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022214340\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerb24\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Kerb24 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean you can probably build one in KSP already. It just needs to be built on Gilly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnce I read in an article that it is not at all easy to build a space elevator, the main problem is the angular momentum that the elevator should withstand, essentially the elevator should be in an orbit that starts from the earth and ends in geostationary orbit, which is practically impossible to achieve. A geostationary orbit is around\u00A0 at 42000km above Earth...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Catto","CreatedById":137773,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-27T23:22:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want water to drip off my vehicle, and parts to be able to get waterlogged as a difficulty option.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf i do a water landing, which is the most likely place to land your craft, i want it to be immersive. If i land my plane in the water, i want it to get WET.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-28T05:13:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224123536\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221651101745\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022137773\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Catto\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Catto said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want water to drip off my vehicle\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot only water, other exotic liquid effects also. And weather.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Catto","CreatedById":137773,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-28T15:24:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224123619\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221651122813\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot only water, other exotic liquid effects also. And weather.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYah\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"t_v","CreatedById":213541,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-28T16:02:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis seems possible to a very limited extent with something as simple as a shader, but if you actually want to simulate the droplets moving over a surface (not even individual droplets, just their general flow in many conditions) it would be one of the hardest and most processing intensive parts of the game. What I could see is a higher reflectivity and some more distortion when parts are wet.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-04-28T16:18:06Z\u0022 title=\u002204/28/2022 04:18  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EApril 28, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by t_v\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-28T16:22:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, just a light shader is enough, for a little more realism when landing during a methane rain storm.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"t_v","CreatedById":213541,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-12T19:04:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone mentioned asteroid bases, I would really love to see absolutely massive asteroids, on the scale of kilometers or even tens of kilometers across, if the engine allows for it. What would be even better would be if they could be moved, which would provide a big end-game challenge for players to move a massive asteroid into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E or something.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Catto","CreatedById":137773,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-12T21:41:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224131130\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221652382266\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022213541\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022t_v\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, t_v said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone mentioned asteroid bases, I would really love to see absolutely massive asteroids, on the scale of kilometers or even tens of kilometers across, if the engine allows for it. What would be even better would be if they could be moved, which would provide a big end-game challenge for players to move a massive asteroid into \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E or something.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgreed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-14T14:02:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKind reminder for new and old forum users to go through this list and think about anything new that could be added.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve updated it constantly with new \u0022maybe borrowed\u0022 ideas (but edits don\u0027t push it to the top of recently interacted posts).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"determinationmaster","CreatedById":209947,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-14T16:18:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224095287\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221645564005\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022214450\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022BekfastDerp13\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/22/2022 at 4:06 PM, BekfastDerp13 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmonths\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni think you mean\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:36px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003EYEARS.\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224095287\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221645564005\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022214450\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022BekfastDerp13\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/22/2022 at 4:06 PM, BekfastDerp13 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ELagrange Points\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0- Complex orbits aren\u0027t going to be in KSP 2, last time I checked.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell, only Rask and Rusk will have the ability for complex orbits. also, i\u0027m pretty confident that with the \u0022higher modding capabilities\u0022 of KSP 2, someone will make a mod for newtonian physics that will completely destroy all but nasa supercomputers!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-14T16:30:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBetter ground anchor, maybe?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-20T13:56:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...long / persistent condensation / exhaust trails\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t believe it took me so long to think about it - would be especially cool in multiplayer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-10-20T13:56:40Z\u0022 title=\u002210/20/2022 01:56  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 20, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Vl3d\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-20T14:52:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224188108\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221666274179\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n55 minutes ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\npersistent condensation / exhaust trails\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight now they disappear if the engine they are tied to is destroyed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-20T20:53:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224188119\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221666277546\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022217956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nazalassa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Nazalassa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224188108\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221666274179\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\npersistent condensation / exhaust trails\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight now they disappear if the engine they are tied to is destroyed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP 2 is a different game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-13T21:33:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI added some more stuff, but I think one of the important ideas is using utility EVA tethers as ropes to rappel down cliffs.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso in the latest gameplay videos the rover wheels do not kick up dust (rooster tails) and do not leave marks on the ground. Footprints should be visible also. It\u0027s an important details for the mood of the game. Vehicles and suits should become dirty and look worn out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/az9nFrnCK60?start=45\u0026amp;feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022[4k, 60 fps] Apollo 16 Lunar Rover \u0026quot;Grand Prix\u0026quot; (1972 April 21, Moon)\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-12-13T21:59:18Z\u0022 title=\u002212/13/2022 09:59  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 13, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Vl3d\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-14T10:30:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI added a suggestion that is very obvious and would be amazing in the game:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EThe Planetarium\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA separate building, easily accessible from Map View and Tracking Station - containing all information from the R\u0026amp;D Facility scientific findings archives and the Tracking Station Knowledge Base. All scientific experiments should unlock interactive graphs, images and animations showing the evolution of the Star System, how the planet was formed, its internal layers, atmosphere / seasons / weather, biosphere and other properties.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomething like augmented map view:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022The Earth can be divided into four layers - crust, mantle, outer core, and inner core.\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.worldatlas.com/r/w1200/upload/21/94/b0/shutterstock-536385025.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Graphic of layers\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022118.42\u0022 height=\u0022650\u0022 srcset=\u0022https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/240/cpsprodpb/922A/production/_85581473_graphic.jpg 240w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/320/cpsprodpb/922A/production/_85581473_graphic.jpg 320w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/480/cpsprodpb/922A/production/_85581473_graphic.jpg 480w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/922A/production/_85581473_graphic.jpg 624w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/922A/production/_85581473_graphic.jpg 800w, https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/922A/production/_85581473_graphic.jpg 976w\u0022 width=\u0022976\u0022 src=\u0022https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/922A/production/_85581473_graphic.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/thumbnails/image/pia21442_updated.jpg\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u00221200\u0022 width=\u00221009\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/thumbnails/image/pia21442_updated.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-19T14:26:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n60 FPS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drakenred65","CreatedById":154503,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-12-20T05:42:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think getting orbital mechanics when flying 4 plus players are flying multiple 255 part ships near a massive colony right trumps your need for frame rate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-12-20T05:42:45Z\u0022 title=\u002212/20/2022 05:42  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 20, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by \u003Ca href=\u0022/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection\u0022 class=\u0022__cf_email__\u0022 data-cfemail=\u0022afebddcec4cac1ddcacb999aefe8c2cec6c381ccc0c2\u0022\u003E[email\u0026#160;protected]\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}